00:31:26,610 --> 00:31:28,077
诡计最多，加斯顿
Takes cheap shots like Gaston

579
00:31:28,312 --> 00:31:31,611
会用那卑劣手段只有你加斯顿
Plans to persecute harmless crackpots like Gaston

580
00:31:31,715 --> 00:31:37,176
很快就能为他举办婚礼喜宴
So his marriage we soon will be celebrating

581
00:31:37,254 --> 00:31:43,352
我的偶像，加斯顿
My, what a guy! Gaston!

582
00:31:47,531 --> 00:31:50,261
难道就没有人肯帮我吗？
Will no one help me?

583
00:31:58,876 --> 00:31:59,535
谁呀？
Who is it?

584
00:31:59,610 --> 00:32:01,202
茶煲太太
Mrs. Potts, dear.

585
00:32:03,080 --> 00:32:05,071
先喝杯热茶
I thought you might like a spot of tea.

586
00:32:05,149 --> 00:32:07,549
你是？你是…
But you're... you're a... Ooh!

587
00:32:08,919 --> 00:32:09,681
小心
Careful.

588
00:32:09,753 --> 00:32:11,186
怎么可能？
This is impossible.

589
00:32:11,255 --> 00:32:13,985
我知道，希望没吓到你
I know it is. But here we are.

590
00:32:14,091 --> 00:32:16,651
妈妈，我说过她很漂亮的，对吧？
I told you she was pretty, Mama, didn't I?

591
00:32:16,727 --> 00:32:19,321
好了，别说了
All right, Chip, now, that'll do.

592
00:32:19,429 --> 00:32:21,488
小心点，别洒了
Slowly now. Don't spill.

593
00:32:22,666 --> 00:32:23,325
谢谢你
Thank you.

594
00:32:24,234 --> 00:32:26,031
你要不要看我玩特技
Want to see me do a trick?

595
00:32:27,604 --> 00:32:28,434
阿齐
Chip!

596
00:32:29,673 --> 00:32:30,537
对不起
Oops. Sorry.

597
00:32:30,641 --> 00:32:33,132
我觉得你是一位非常勇敢的女孩子
That was a very brave thing you did, my dear.

598
00:32:33,243 --> 00:32:34,733
我们都是这么想的
We all think so.

599
00:32:34,812 --> 00:32:36,404
但是我失去了我爸爸
But I've lost my father,

600
00:32:36,513 --> 00:32:38,344
我的梦想，所有的一切
my dreams... everything.

601
00:32:38,415 --> 00:32:40,576
开心一点
Cheer up, child.

602
00:32:40,651 --> 00:32:43,085
事情总会好转的
It'll turn out all right in the end.

603
00:32:43,153 --> 00:32:44,518
放心吧
You'll see. Oh, listen to me.

604
00:32:44,621 --> 00:32:48,421
晚餐的时候你可以跟他好好地聊聊
Jabbering on while there's a supper
to get on the table.

605
00:32:48,525 --> 00:32:49,457
阿齐
Chip!

606
00:32:50,594 --> 00:32:51,720
拜拜
Bye.

607
00:32:52,095 --> 00:32:52,857
好了
Well, now, 

608
00:32:52,963 --> 00:32:54,555
我们晚餐的时候该穿什么呢？
what shall we dress you in for dinner?

609
00:32:55,365 --> 00:32:57,299
让我看看柜子里有些什么衣服
Oh, let's see what I got in my drawers.

610
00:32:58,135 --> 00:33:00,160
真不好意思
Ooh! How embarrassing.

611
00:33:02,506 --> 00:33:03,837
有了
Ah, here we are.

612
00:33:03,907 --> 00:33:05,898
穿这件会让你看起来令人着迷
You'll look ravishing in this one.

613
00:33:06,009 --> 00:33:07,203
谢谢你的好意
That's very kind of you, 

614
00:33:07,311 --> 00:33:09,404
可是我不会跟他一块儿吃晚餐的
but... I'm not going to dinner.

615
00:33:10,046 --> 00:33:12,071
那怎么行
Oh, but you must.

616
00:33:12,182 --> 00:33:17,449
小姐，晚餐好了
Dinner is served.

617
00:33:19,389 --> 00:33:21,220
怎么这么久？
What's taking so long?

618
00:33:21,324 --> 00:33:23,121
我跟她说过要她下来的
I told her to come down.

619
00:33:23,226 --> 00:33:24,750
她为什么还不来？
Why isn't she here yet?

620
00:33:24,861 --> 00:33:26,795
有点耐性嘛，主人
Oh, try to be patient, sir.

621
00:33:26,863 --> 00:33:30,264
可怜她在一天之内失去了父亲跟自由
The girl has lost her father
and her freedom, all in one day.

622
00:33:30,366 --> 00:33:31,731
主人，你有没有想过
Master, have you thought

623
00:33:31,834 --> 00:33:34,632
这个善良美丽的女孩也许会解开咒语？
that perhaps this girl could
be the one to break the spell?

624
00:33:34,737 --> 00:33:36,398
我当然想过
Of course I have.

625
00:33:36,506 --> 00:33:37,473
我又不是傻瓜
I'm not a fool.

626
00:33:37,574 --> 00:33:38,404
好极了
Good!

627
00:33:38,474 --> 00:33:41,966
你爱她，她也爱你
So, you fall in love with her,
she falls in love with you

628
00:33:42,078 --> 00:33:43,943
然后，咒语就解开了
and poof! The spell is broken.

629
00:33:44,047 --> 00:33:45,947
我们就可以变回人类了
We'll be human again by midnight.

630
00:33:46,049 --> 00:33:48,882
这事不容易，需要时间啊
Ooh, it's not that easy, Lumiere.
These things take time.

631
00:33:48,952 --> 00:33:51,147
但是玫瑰花已经开始凋谢了
But the rose has already begun to wilt.

632
00:33:51,921 --> 00:33:55,982
没有用的，她那么美
Oh, it's no use. She's so beautiful,

633
00:33:56,092 --> 00:33:57,184
我呢？
and I'm... Well, look at me!

634
00:33:59,662 --> 00:34:02,495
所以你要想办法让她了解你
Oh, you must help her to see past all that.

635
00:34:02,831 --> 00:34:03,820
我不知怎么做
I don't know how.

636
00:34:04,767 --> 00:34:07,327
先把你凶恶的外表改一改
Well, you can start by making yourself more presentable.

637
00:34:07,403 --> 00:34:09,462
站直了，像个绅士一样
Straighten up. Try to act like a gentleman.

638
00:34:09,538 --> 00:34:11,005
当她进来的时候
Ah, yes. When she comes in

639
00:34:11,073 --> 00:34:13,803
给她一个礼貌愉快的笑容
give her a dashing, debonair smile.

640
00:34:13,909 --> 00:34:15,171
快，笑给我看看
Come, come, show me the smile.

641
00:34:16,178 --> 00:34:17,805
这样会吓着她的
But don't frighten the poor girl.

642
00:34:17,880 --> 00:34:20,371
以你的才智给她一个好印象
Impress her with your rapier wit.

643
00:34:20,482 --> 00:34:21,380
而且要温柔
But be gentle.

644
00:34:21,483 --> 00:34:22,814
多多赞美她
Shower her with compliments.

645
00:34:22,918 --> 00:34:23,816
可是要有诚意
But be sincere.

646
00:34:23,886 --> 00:34:27,652
最重要的还得要控制自己的脾气
And above all... You must control your temper!

647
00:34:28,657 --> 00:34:29,487
她来了
Here she is!

648
00:34:31,993 --> 00:34:33,051
晚安
Good evening.

649
00:34:34,528 --> 00:34:36,189
她在哪里？
Well, where is she?

650
00:34:36,497 --> 00:34:38,397
谁？
Who? Oh.

651
00:34:38,466 --> 00:34:39,125
那个女孩？
The girl, yes.

652
00:34:39,200 --> 00:34:41,464
是，有个女孩
The... girl.

653
00:34:41,535 --> 00:34:42,331
事实上
Well, actually,

654
00:34:42,536 --> 00:34:45,130
她现在…正处于…
she's in the process of...

655
00:34:45,206 --> 00:34:46,332
这种情况…
Circumstances being 

656
00:34:46,407 --> 00:34:49,501
她…她不来了
what they are... She's not coming.

657
00:34:50,578 --> 00:34:51,670
什么？
What?!

658
00:34:52,313 --> 00:34:55,510
主人，主人
But, Your Grace!

659
00:34:55,616 --> 00:34:57,379
请你不要太急躁
Your Eminence!

660
00:35:00,354 --> 00:35:01,981
我说过要你下来吃晚饭
I thought I told you to come down to dinner!

661
00:35:02,089 --> 00:35:03,283
我不饿
I'm not hungry.

662
00:35:04,258 --> 00:35:05,555
你快点出来
You come out, or I'll...

663
00:35:05,626 --> 00:35:07,491
不然我打烂这扇门
I'll... I'll break down the door!

664
00:35:07,561 --> 00:35:09,358
主人，也许我说得不对
Master... I could be wrong,

665
00:35:09,430 --> 00:35:13,890
但这种方法是不能打动一个女孩的芳心的
but that may not be the best way
to win the girl's affections.

666
00:35:14,001 --> 00:35:17,459
如果你能像个绅士，也许会好一点
Please attempt to be a gentleman.

667
00:35:17,571 --> 00:35:20,301
她实在是太不可理喻了
But she is being so difficult.

668
00:35:20,408 --> 00:35:23,434
温柔…
Gently, gently.

669
00:35:24,812 --> 00:35:26,211
你下来吃饭吗？
Will you come down to dinner?

670
00:35:26,280 --> 00:35:27,804
不要
No.  Hmm?  Ah, ah, ah!

671
00:35:28,649 --> 00:35:30,583
礼貌、绅士
Suave, genteel.

672
00:35:30,818 --> 00:35:34,686
不知道我有没有这份荣幸…
It would give me great pleasure

673
00:35:34,755 --> 00:35:36,814
跟你一块儿共进晚餐？
if you would join me for dinner.

674
00:35:36,924 --> 00:35:37,982
说“请”
We say please.

675
00:35:38,993 --> 00:35:40,392
-请… -不要，谢谢
Please.  No, thank you!

676
00:35:40,494 --> 00:35:41,961
你不可能永远在里面
You can't stay in there forever!

677
00:35:42,063 --> 00:35:42,722
我可以
Yes, I can.

678
00:35:42,797 --> 00:35:47,325
好，你就在里面挨饿
Fine. Then go ahead and starve!

679
00:35:47,401 --> 00:35:49,801
她如果不肯跟我吃晚饭
If she doesn't eat with me,

680
00:35:50,037 --> 00:35:52,267
她就永远没有饭吃
then she doesn't eat at all.

681
00:35:55,476 --> 00:35:56,568
天啊
Oh, dear.

682
00:35:56,644 --> 00:35:58,445
他的脾气怎么还是不改？
That didn't go very well at all, did it?

683
00:35:58,445 --> 00:36:01,414
卢米亚，你在这守着
Lumiere, stand watch at the door

684
00:36:01,482 --> 00:36:02,710
如果有任何情况
and inform me at once

685
00:36:02,816 --> 00:36:04,681
就马上来通知我听见没有？
if there is the slightest change.

686
00:36:04,785 --> 00:36:06,616
这件事就交给我了
You can count on me, mon capitan.

687
00:36:07,621 --> 00:36:10,317
我看我们还是先下楼
Well, we might as well go downstairs

688
00:36:10,391 --> 00:36:12,086
下去收拾收拾吧
and start cleaning up.

689
00:36:13,060 --> 00:36:15,551
我好声好气地请她都被拒绝了
I ask nicely, but she refuses.

690
00:36:15,663 --> 00:36:17,688
她到底想要我怎么样？
Well, what does she want me to do...

691
00:36:17,765 --> 00:36:18,561
求她？
beg?

692
00:36:19,600 --> 00:36:20,726
我要看那个女孩
Show me the girl.

693
00:36:23,571 --> 00:36:27,029
一旦你了解他就会明白他不是个坏人
Well, the master's really not so bad
once you get to know him.

694
00:36:27,107 --> 00:36:29,132
你为什么不给他一个机会呢？
Why don't you give him a chance?

695
00:36:29,243 --> 00:36:30,938
我不想了解他
I don't want to get to know him.

696
00:36:31,045 --> 00:36:31,713
我才不要跟他有任何牵连
I don't want to have anything to do with him!

697
00:36:31,713 --> 00:36:33,305
我才不要跟他有任何牵连
I don't want to have anything to do with him!

698
00:36:35,983 --> 00:36:37,712
我只是自欺欺人
I'm just fooling myself.

699
00:36:37,819 --> 00:36:40,310
她不会把我当正常人看的
She'll never see me as anything...

700
00:36:40,988 --> 00:36:42,216
我永远是野兽
but a monster.

701
00:36:47,729 --> 00:36:48,855
没希望的
It's hopeless.

702
00:37:07,014 --> 00:37:08,879
-不要 -要
Oh, no!  Oh, yes!

703
00:37:08,983 --> 00:37:09,711
不要
Oh, no!

704
00:37:09,784 --> 00:37:11,581
要…
Oh, yes, yes, yes!

705
00:37:11,652 --> 00:37:14,450
人家以前被你烫过
I've been burned by you before.

706
00:37:17,291 --> 00:37:19,316
我的天啊，她跑出来了
Zut, alors! She has emerged!

707
00:37:23,931 --> 00:37:28,902
好了，快跟哥哥姐姐一块进橱子里去吧
Come on, Chip, into the cupboard
with your brothers and sisters.

708
00:37:28,902 --> 00:37:30,563
人家不想睡嘛
But I'm not sleepy.

709
00:37:30,804 --> 00:37:31,896
该睡了
Yes, you are.

710
00:37:31,972 --> 00:37:33,405
不，我不要
No, I'm not.

711
00:37:34,208 --> 00:37:36,142
我忙了一整天
I work and I slave all day long

712
00:37:36,210 --> 00:37:37,199
是为了什么？
and for what?

713
00:37:37,611 --> 00:37:40,341
白白浪费我那么好的烹调技术
A culinary masterpiece gone to waste.

714
00:37:40,447 --> 00:37:41,846
你不要再抱怨了
Oh, stop your grousing.

715
00:37:41,915 --> 00:37:43,644
今天每个人都很累了
It's been a long night for all of us.

716
00:37:43,751 --> 00:37:46,914
依我看她也太过份了
Well, if you ask me, she was just being stubborn.

717
00:37:47,021 --> 00:37:48,511
我们主人都已经说请了
After all, he did say please.

718
00:37:48,622 --> 00:37:51,250
他一定要试着控制脾气
But if the master doesn't learn to control that temper

719
00:37:51,325 --> 00:37:52,053
否则他永远…
he'll never break...

720
00:37:52,159 --> 00:37:55,424
真…真高兴见到你
Splendid to see you out and about, Mademoiselle.

721
00:37:55,496 --> 00:37:56,895
我是葛士华
I am Cogsworth,

722
00:37:56,964 --> 00:37:58,625
是这里的总管
head of the household.

723
00:38:00,567 --> 00:38:01,295
他是卢米亚
This is Lumiere.

724
00:38:01,402 --> 00:38:03,563
认识你是我的荣幸
Enchante, cherie.

725
00:38:03,671 --> 00:38:06,902
如果有什么需要我为你服务的话
If there's... Stop that! ...anything we... Please!

726
00:38:06,974 --> 00:38:09,738
尽量吩咐
Can do to make your stay more comfortable.

727
00:38:10,277 --> 00:38:11,539
我有点饿了
I am a little hungry.

728
00:38:11,645 --> 00:38:13,510
听见了没有？
You are? Hear that? 

729
00:38:13,580 --> 00:38:14,239
她饿了
She's hungry.

730
00:38:14,348 --> 00:38:15,246
快生火
Stoke the fire.

731
00:38:15,783 --> 00:38:17,478
拿出银器，叫醒瓷碟
Break out the silver. Wake the china.

732
00:38:17,584 --> 00:38:19,984
不要忘记主人的交待
Remember what the master said.

733
00:38:20,087 --> 00:38:20,951
我才不管呢
Oh, pishposh.

734
00:38:21,021 --> 00:38:23,319
反正我是不会让孩子挨饿的
I'm not about to let the poor child go hungry.

735
00:38:23,424 --> 00:38:24,721
好吧
All right, fine.

736
00:38:24,958 --> 00:38:26,084
一杯水一个面包就行了
Glass of water, crust of bread, and then...

737
00:38:26,160 --> 00:38:28,996
葛士华，我真服了你
Cogsworth, I am surprised at you.

738
00:38:28,996 --> 00:38:30,156
她不是犯人
She is not a prisoner.

739
00:38:30,264 --> 00:38:31,492
她是我们的贵客
She's our guest.

740
00:38:31,765 --> 00:38:33,630
我们一定要让她觉得亲切
We must make her feel welcome here.

741
00:38:33,701 --> 00:38:35,396
小姐，这边请
Right this way, Mademoiselle.

742
00:38:35,502 --> 00:38:37,231
好吧，小声一点
Well, keep it down.

743
00:38:37,471 --> 00:38:38,563
要是被主人听见了
If the master finds out about this

744
00:38:38,672 --> 00:38:39,764
我们就惨了
it will be our necks.

745
00:38:39,873 --> 00:38:42,000
当然，当然
Of course, of course.

746
00:38:42,076 --> 00:38:44,943
可是一顿丰盛的晚餐怎么能没有音乐
But what is dinner without a little music?

747
00:38:45,546 --> 00:38:46,843
音乐？
Music?

748
00:38:48,615 --> 00:38:50,515
亲爱的小姐
Ma chere mademoiselle.

749
00:38:50,617 --> 00:38:54,144
很荣幸有这个机会为你服务
It is with deepest pride and greatest pleasure

750
00:38:54,221 --> 00:38:55,984
诚心欢迎你
that we welcome you tonight.

751
00:38:56,056 --> 00:38:57,358
现在请先上座
And now we invite you to relax.

752
00:38:57,358 --> 00:38:58,689
现在请先上座
And now we invite you to relax.

753
00:38:58,759 --> 00:39:00,124
放松心情
Let us pull up a chair

754
00:39:00,227 --> 00:39:02,787
享受本餐厅特别为你准备的…
as the dining room proudly presents...

755
00:39:03,731 --> 00:39:04,891
晚餐
your dinner.

756
00:39:06,533 --> 00:39:11,300
请享用，小贵客
Be... our... guest, Be our guest

757
00:39:11,372 --> 00:39:13,704
我们可爱的贵客
Put our service to the test

758
00:39:13,807 --> 00:39:16,002
请把餐巾先围好
Tie your napkin 'round your neck, cherie

759
00:39:16,076 --> 00:39:18,408
让我们来为你服务
And we provide the rest

760
00:39:18,479 --> 00:39:22,916
热汤先上，服务至上
Soup du jour, Hot hors d'oeuvres 
Why, we only live to serve

761
00:39:23,016 --> 00:39:25,382
再请尝些小西点它味道既甜又美
Try the gray stuff, It's delicious

762
00:39:25,486 --> 00:39:27,681
不要怀疑，问问餐具
Don't believe me, ask the dishes

763
00:39:27,755 --> 00:39:29,950
它们能唱，它们能跳
They can sing, they can dance

764
00:39:30,057 --> 00:39:32,252
你现在是在法国
After all, Miss, this is France

765
00:39:32,493 --> 00:39:36,293
想要饱餐一顿就到这里来
And a dinner here is never second best

766
00:39:36,397 --> 00:39:38,797
首先请打开菜单
Go on, unfold your menu

767
00:39:38,899 --> 00:39:40,958
选出你所想要
Take a glance and then

768
00:39:41,068 --> 00:39:43,229
请享用，小贵客
You'll be our guest, Oui, our guest,

769
00:39:43,337 --> 00:39:44,565
请享用
Be our guest

770
00:39:45,372 --> 00:39:47,533
