It's past your bedtime.

1149
01:05:30,427 --> 01:05:31,416
晚安
Good night, love.

1150
01:05:56,052 --> 01:05:56,916
贝儿
Belle?

1151
01:05:59,756 --> 01:06:02,589
你在这里会觉得快乐吗？
Are you... happy here with me?

1152
01:06:03,259 --> 01:06:04,317
当然
Yes.

1153
01:06:09,065 --> 01:06:10,464
怎么了？
What is it?

1154
01:06:11,768 --> 01:06:14,168
我好希望能再见到我爸爸
If only I could see my father again

1155
01:06:14,270 --> 01:06:16,932
只要一眼，我好想念他
just for a moment. I miss him so much.

1156
01:06:22,579 --> 01:06:24,604
我有办法
There is a way.

1157
01:06:27,450 --> 01:06:32,444
这面镜子可以让你看到任何你想看到的事情
This mirror will show you anything...
anything you wish to see.

1158
01:06:33,022 --> 01:06:34,819
我希望能看到我父亲
I'd like to see my father,

1159
01:06:34,891 --> 01:06:35,880
好吗？
please.

1160
01:06:42,799 --> 01:06:43,527
爸爸
Papa?

1161
01:06:44,667 --> 01:06:47,261
不，他生病了
Oh, no. He's sick.

1162
01:06:47,370 --> 01:06:48,359
他也许会死
He may be dying

1163
01:06:48,438 --> 01:06:49,735
他那么孤单无助
and he's all alone.

1164
01:06:56,479 --> 01:06:59,676
那…那你该回去照顾他
Then, you must go to him.

1165
01:07:00,016 --> 01:07:01,005
你说…什么？
What did you say?

1166
01:07:01,417 --> 01:07:02,941
你可以走了
I release you.

1167
01:07:03,052 --> 01:07:04,519
你不再是我的犯人了
You are no longer my prisoner.

1168
01:07:04,621 --> 01:07:07,215
你是说，我自由了
You mean... I'm free?

1169
01:07:08,091 --> 01:07:09,353
是的
Yes.

1170
01:07:09,559 --> 01:07:12,050
谢谢你
Oh, thank you.

1171
01:07:12,162 --> 01:07:13,322
爸爸，振作点
Hold on, Papa.

1172
01:07:13,396 --> 01:07:14,761
我马上就回来了
I'm on my way.

1173
01:07:17,433 --> 01:07:19,094
带着它吧
Take it with you

1174
01:07:19,202 --> 01:07:21,830
这样你可以回忆一下这里
so you'll always have a way to look back

1175
01:07:22,071 --> 01:07:23,436
希望你记得我
and remember me.

1176
01:07:27,377 --> 01:07:29,902
谢谢你能谅解他对我的重要
Thank you for understanding how much he needs me.

1177
01:07:38,888 --> 01:07:40,446
主人
Well, Your Highness,

1178
01:07:40,557 --> 01:07:43,788
这每一件事情都进行得很顺利
I must say everything is going just swimmingly.

1179
01:07:43,893 --> 01:07:46,589
我知道你是绝对没有问题的
I knew you had it in you.

1180
01:07:46,663 --> 01:07:47,322
我让她走了
I let her go.

1181
01:07:48,798 --> 01:07:51,665
是的，是的，那太好了
Yes, yes. Splen...

1182
01:07:51,768 --> 01:07:53,998
你…什么？
You what? 

1183
01:07:54,103 --> 01:07:55,661
你怎么能这样做呢？
How could you do that?

1184
01:07:55,905 --> 01:07:57,133
我不得不
I had to.

1185
01:07:57,240 --> 01:08:00,232
但…但…为什么呢？
Yes, but... Why?

1186
01:08:00,577 --> 01:08:03,876
因为我爱她
Because... I love her.

1187
01:08:03,980 --> 01:08:05,572
他做了什么？
He did what?

1188
01:08:05,648 --> 01:08:08,048
没错，他答应让她走了
Yes. I'm afraid it's true.

1189
01:08:08,117 --> 01:08:09,744
她要走吗？
She's going away?

1190
01:08:09,853 --> 01:08:11,844
就只差那么一点点了
But he was so close.

1191
01:08:11,955 --> 01:08:13,786
不管怎么说
After all this time,

1192
01:08:13,890 --> 01:08:16,415
他终于学会了怎么去爱人
he's finally learned to love.

1193
01:08:16,526 --> 01:08:17,550
那咒语是不是
That's it, then.

1194
01:08:17,627 --> 01:08:19,185
就应该解开了？
That should break the spell.

1195
01:08:19,295 --> 01:08:20,762
还是没用的
But it's not enough.

1196
01:08:20,830 --> 01:08:23,264
贝儿也得爱他才行啊
She has to love him in return.

1197
01:08:24,033 --> 01:08:25,591
这一切都太迟了
Now it's too late.

1198
01:08:35,178 --> 01:08:38,113
爸爸，爸爸
Papa! Papa!

1199
01:08:52,662 --> 01:08:53,686
他们回来了
Ooh. They're back.

1200
01:08:56,466 --> 01:08:57,455
贝儿
Belle?

1201
01:08:59,135 --> 01:09:02,070
没事了，爸爸，我回来了
It's all right, Papa. I'm home.

1202
01:09:03,072 --> 01:09:06,200
我以为再也看不见你了
I thought I'd never see you again.

1203
01:09:06,309 --> 01:09:08,072
我好想你啊
I missed you so much.

1204
01:09:08,144 --> 01:09:09,008
那野兽
But the Beast?

1205
01:09:09,112 --> 01:09:10,636
你怎么逃出来的？
Did you... how did you escape?

1206
01:09:10,713 --> 01:09:12,647
我不是逃走的，爸爸
I didn't escape, Papa.

1207
01:09:12,849 --> 01:09:13,713
他让我走的
He let me go.

1208
01:09:13,816 --> 01:09:15,147
那只可怕的野兽？
That horrible beast?

1209
01:09:15,251 --> 01:09:17,310
他现在不一样了，爸爸
But he's different now, Papa.

1210
01:09:17,420 --> 01:09:19,854
他改变了好多哦
He's changed somehow.

1211
01:09:27,163 --> 01:09:28,721
一个偷渡客啊
Oh. A stowaway.

1212
01:09:29,666 --> 01:09:31,497
小家伙
Why, hello there, little fella.

1213
01:09:31,601 --> 01:09:33,967
真没想到还能再看见你
Didn't think I'd see you again.

1214
01:09:34,037 --> 01:09:36,631
贝儿，你为什么要走？
Belle, why'd you go away?

1215
01:09:36,706 --> 01:09:38,799
你不喜欢我们了吗？
Don't you like us anymore?

1216
01:09:38,875 --> 01:09:41,275
阿齐，我当然喜欢
Oh, Chip, of course I do.

1217
01:09:41,344 --> 01:09:42,436
可是因为…
It's just...

1218
01:09:45,515 --> 01:09:46,311
请问有事吗？
May I help you?

1219
01:09:46,382 --> 01:09:49,010
我们是来接你父亲的
I've come to collect your father.

1220
01:09:49,085 --> 01:09:50,109
我父亲？
My father?

1221
01:09:50,219 --> 01:09:52,016
小姐，你别担心
Don't worry, Mademoiselle.

1222
01:09:52,088 --> 01:09:54,352
我们会好好照顾他的
We'll take good care of him.

1223
01:09:55,391 --> 01:09:56,949
我父亲不是疯子
My father's not crazy.

1224
01:09:57,060 --> 01:09:58,857
他像疯子一样胡说八道
He was raving like a lunatic.

1225
01:09:58,962 --> 01:10:00,623
我们都听到了，对不对？
We all heard him, didn't we?

1226
01:10:03,032 --> 01:10:05,023
不，我不准你们…
No, I won't let you.

1227
01:10:05,101 --> 01:10:07,331
-贝儿 -莫维斯？
Belle? Maurice,

1228
01:10:07,403 --> 01:10:08,893
老头子，你再说一遍
tell us again, old man.

1229
01:10:09,305 --> 01:10:11,739
那个野兽有多大啊？
Just how big was the beast?

1230
01:10:12,709 --> 01:10:16,167
它…它…很大
He was... I mean, he was... he was... enormous.

1231
01:10:16,279 --> 01:10:17,974
大概有八英尺
I-I'd say at least eight...

1232
01:10:18,081 --> 01:10:19,878
不…超过十英尺吧
No, more like ten feet.

1233
01:10:22,118 --> 01:10:24,586
他不疯，那谁才是疯子啊？
Well, you don't get much crazier than that.

1234
01:10:25,722 --> 01:10:28,156
是真的，真的
It's true, I tell you.

1235
01:10:28,224 --> 01:10:29,782
把他带走
Get him out of here.

1236
01:10:29,859 --> 01:10:31,156
放开我
Let go of me.

1237
01:10:31,427 --> 01:10:32,086
不
No!

1238
01:10:32,161 --> 01:10:34,220
你们不能这么做
You can't do this.

1239
01:10:34,897 --> 01:10:36,330
可怜的贝儿
Poor Belle.

1240
01:10:36,399 --> 01:10:38,026
你爸爸怎么会是个疯子啊
It's a shame about your father.

1241
01:10:38,134 --> 01:10:40,034
你知道他没有疯的对不对
You know he's not crazy, Gaston.

1242
01:10:40,703 --> 01:10:42,796
我倒是可以想想办法
Hmm, I might be able to clear up this...

1243
01:10:42,872 --> 01:10:45,067
帮你澄清这个误会
little misunderstanding.

1244
01:10:45,141 --> 01:10:46,802
-只要… -只要什么？
If... If what?

1245
01:10:46,909 --> 01:10:48,740
只要你肯嫁给我
If you marry me.

1246
01:10:48,845 --> 01:10:51,177
-什么？ -一个字，贝儿
What?  One little word, Belle.

1247
01:10:51,247 --> 01:10:52,475
只要你肯说那一个字
That's all it takes.

1248
01:10:52,582 --> 01:10:54,174
-休想  -随你便了
Never.  Have it your way.

1249
01:10:54,550 --> 01:10:58,213
-贝儿  -放开我
Belle.  Let go of me.

1250
01:10:58,321 --> 01:11:00,881
我可以证明我父亲不是疯子
My father's not crazy and I can prove it.

1251
01:11:01,391 --> 01:11:02,380
让我看野兽
Show me the Beast.

1252
01:11:07,830 --> 01:11:08,819
他会伤人吗？
Is it dangerous?

1253
01:11:08,898 --> 01:11:11,230
不会的，他从来没有伤过人
Oh, no, no, he'd never hurt anyone.

1254
01:11:11,300 --> 01:11:13,063
我知道他样子长得很可怕
Please, I know he looks vicious,

1255
01:11:13,169 --> 01:11:16,195
但是他很仁慈又绅士
but he's really kind and gentle.

1256
01:11:16,305 --> 01:11:17,329
他是我的朋友
He's my friend.

1257
01:11:17,407 --> 01:11:18,396
如果我没猜错
If I didn't know better

1258
01:11:18,474 --> 01:11:21,534
你看起来跟那个怪物好像很有感情啊
I'd think you had feelings for this monster.

1259
01:11:21,644 --> 01:11:23,339
他不是怪物，加斯顿
He's no monster, Gaston.

1260
01:11:23,446 --> 01:11:24,208
你才是
You are.

1261
01:11:25,481 --> 01:11:28,314
我看这个女孩跟她爸爸一样疯了
She's as crazy as the old man.

1262
01:11:28,518 --> 01:11:31,783
野兽会在夜里偷走你们的孩子
The Beast will make off with your children.
He'll come after them in the night.

1263
01:11:31,888 --> 01:11:35,255
-不会  -只有杀了他才安全
No!  We're not safe
till his head is mounted on my wall.

1264
01:11:35,391 --> 01:11:37,120
我建议我们杀了他
I say we kill the Beast!

1265
01:11:38,428 --> 01:11:39,986
野兽不能让他活
We're not safe until he's dead

1266
01:11:40,096 --> 01:11:41,586
晚上他会来害人
He'll come stalking us at night

1267
01:11:41,697 --> 01:11:43,130
要是让他吃掉孩子
Set to sacrifice our children

1268
01:11:43,232 --> 01:11:44,995
不如马上除掉他
To his monstrous appetite

1269
01:11:45,101 --> 01:11:46,762
他在小城出现
He'll wreak havoc on our village

1270
01:11:46,869 --> 01:11:48,734
就会扰乱我们的生活
If we let him wander free

1271
01:11:48,805 --> 01:11:52,639
是我们该行动的时候
So it's time to take some action, boys

1272
01:11:52,708 --> 01:11:57,668
请大家跟我来
It's time to follow me

1273
01:11:59,415 --> 01:12:02,441
过沼泽，穿森林  走过黑暗，走过阴影
Through the mist, through the woods
Through the darkness and the shadows

1274
01:12:02,518 --> 01:12:05,453
一个恶梦但却令我兴奋
It's a nightmare, but it's one exciting ride

1275
01:12:05,555 --> 01:12:07,182
祈求天指引我
Say a prayer, then we're there

1276
01:12:07,290 --> 01:12:08,985
过了吊桥就是城堡
at the drawbridge of a castle

1277
01:12:09,092 --> 01:12:12,425
有个怪物一定要把他除掉
And there's something truly terrible inside

1278
01:12:12,528 --> 01:12:14,052
是野兽，他可恶
It's a beast, he's got fangs, 

1279
01:12:14,163 --> 01:12:15,391
危害人类
razor-sharp ones

1280
01:12:15,465 --> 01:12:18,593
他残暴，凶猛，没人性
Massive paws, killer claws, for the feast

1281
01:12:18,701 --> 01:12:20,566
他怒吼，他疯狂
Hear him roar, see him foam

1282
01:12:20,670 --> 01:12:22,228
但我们一定要杀掉他
But we're not coming home 

1283
01:12:22,338 --> 01:12:26,331
让他死，杀野兽
Till he's dead, Good and dead, Kill the Beast!

1284
01:12:26,409 --> 01:12:28,036
不，我不准你们伤害他
No, I won't let you do this.

1285
01:12:28,111 --> 01:12:30,477
假如你不跟我们一起 就是反对我们
If you're not with us, you're against us.

1286
01:12:30,580 --> 01:12:32,013
把那个老头带来
Bring the old man.

1287
01:12:32,115 --> 01:12:33,514
放开我
Get your hands off me.

1288
01:12:33,749 --> 01:12:36,047
我们也不会让你去通知那个野兽
We can't have them running off
to warn the creature.

1289
01:12:36,285 --> 01:12:37,445
放我们出去
Let us out!

1290
01:12:37,553 --> 01:12:39,783
现在要出发去抓那个野兽
We'll rid the village of this beast.

1291
01:12:39,889 --> 01:12:41,288
谁愿意跟我一起去？
Who's with me?

1292
01:12:43,726 --> 01:12:44,920
燃火把，快上马
Raise your torch, mount your horse

1293
01:12:45,027 --> 01:12:46,619
带好武器勇敢向前冲
Screw your courage to the sticking place

1294
01:12:46,696 --> 01:12:49,824
我们让加斯顿来作领导
We're counting on Gaston to lead the way

1295
01:12:49,932 --> 01:12:51,297
过沼泽，穿森林
Through the mist, through the wood

1296
01:12:51,367 --> 01:12:52,891
走过黑暗阴影
Where, within a haunted castle

1297
01:12:52,969 --> 01:12:55,961
有个怪物在那城堡
Something's lurking that you don't see every day

1298
01:12:56,205 --> 01:12:59,299
他是像山一样高大的野兽
It's a beast, one as tall as a mountain

1299
01:12:59,542 --> 01:13:02,773
不休息直到他倒下去
We won't rest till he's good and deceased

1300
01:13:02,879 --> 01:13:04,506
走啊，冲啊
Sally forth, tally ho

1301
01:13:04,614 --> 01:13:06,172
握紧你的剑，拿起你的弓
Grab your sword, grab your bow

1302
01:13:06,282 --> 01:13:07,772
赞美主，我们出发
Praise the Lord, and here we go.

1303
01:13:07,884 --> 01:13:09,511
我们要让城堡倒下
We'll lay siege to the castle

1304
01:13:09,619 --> 01:13:11,246
带回他的头
and bring back his head!

1305
01:13:12,155 --> 01:13:13,645
我一定要去通知野兽
I have to warn the Beast.

1306
01:13:13,723 --> 01:13:15,315
都是我惹的祸
This is all my fault.

1307
01:13:15,391 --> 01:13:17,086
爸爸，我们该怎么办？
Oh, Papa, what are we going to do?

1308
01:13:17,160 --> 01:13:18,491
不是的…
Now, now.

1309
01:13:18,694 --> 01:13:20,355
我们要赶紧想办法
We'll think of something.

1310
01:13:27,637 --> 01:13:34,372
我们不了解可怕的野兽而心生恐惧
We don't like what we don't understand
In fact, it scares us And this monster
is mysterious at least

1311
01:13:34,477 --> 01:13:35,842
拿起枪，拿起刀
Bring your guns, bring your knives

1312
01:13:35,945 --> 01:13:37,503
拯救妇女小孩
Save your children and your wives

1313
01:13:37,613 --> 01:13:40,673
恢复我们小城的可爱
We'll save our village and our lives

1314
01:13:40,783 --> 01:13:42,080
杀死野兽
We'll kill the Beast!

1315
01:13:42,852 --> 01:13:46,015
我们根本就不该抱太大希望的
I knew it was foolish to get our hopes up.

1316
01:13:46,122 --> 01:13:48,784
也许她从来没有出现过比较好
Maybe it would have been better
if she'd never come at all.

1317
01:13:50,059 --> 01:13:51,185
可能吗？
Could it be?

1318
01:13:51,294 --> 01:13:52,022
是她吗？
Is it she?

1319
01:13:52,395 --> 01:13:54,522
有人侵入
Sacre bleu! Invaders.

1320
01:13:54,630 --> 01:13:55,756
有敌人
Encroachers.

1321
01:13:55,865 --> 01:13:57,196
他们有魔镜
And they have the mirror.

1322
01:13:57,300 --> 01:13:58,164
快去通知主人
Warn the master.

1323
01:13:58,234 --> 01:14:00,259
要准备应战了
If it's a fight they want, we'll be ready for them.

1324
01:14:00,369 --> 01:14:01,631
有谁跟我来？
Who's with me?

1325
01:14:02,371 --> 01:14:04,168
你们可以拿任何你们想要的东西
Take whatever booty you can find

1326
01:14:04,240 --> 01:14:07,437
但记住，那个野兽是我的
but remember, the Beast is mine!

1327
01:14:07,543 --> 01:14:10,910
我们不怕任何困难危险
Lights ablaze, banners high, We go marching into battle

1328
01:14:11,013 --> 01:14:13,709
坚持到底跟他们作战
Unafraid, although the danger just increased

1329
01:14:13,816 --> 01:14:15,408
高举旗，大声唱
Raise the flag, sing the song

1330
01:14:15,518 --> 01:14:20,012
我们五十个人 强壮有力一定会成功
Here we come, we're 50 strong
And 50 Frenchmen can't be wrong

1331
01:14:20,089 --> 01:14:21,181
杀死野兽
Let's kill the Beast!

1332
01:14:22,625 --> 01:14:24,024
主人陛下
Pardon me, Master?

1333
01:14:24,126 --> 01:14:25,354
不要烦我
Leave me in peace.

1334
01:14:25,461 --> 01:14:27,929
但是有人攻打城堡啊
But, sir, the castle is under attack.

1335
01:14:28,431 --> 01:14:31,093
杀野兽…杀野兽…
Kill the Beast! Kill the Beast!

1336
01:14:31,634 --> 01:14:32,965
这样是不行的
This isn't working.

1337
01:14:33,069 --> 01:14:34,036
卢米亚
Oh, Lumiere,

1338
01:14:34,136 --> 01:14:35,535
我们快想办法啊
we must do something.

